  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together coconut oil, honey, lemon juice, ginger powder, turmeric powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chopped peaches to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated peaches onto the soaked bamboo skewers.",
    "Place the skewers on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Roast the peach skewers in the preheated oven for 20 minutes, or until caramelized and slightly charred.",
    "Remove the skewers from the oven and sprinkle with chopped fresh mint leaves.",
    "Serve the roasted peach skewers warm or at room temperature."
